    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/TherapistList.tsx` to handle therapist setup and settings. It will allow users to manage the 30-therapist roster, configure their rehabilitation specialty role (PT/OT/ST), select their preferred 60-minute lunch/break start window (consecutive 3 slots), and designate specific \"Busy / Off-duty\" slots where they cannot be assigned. It includes search, filters, a creation modal, and instant deletion."
